definitions.definition: A person of the indigenous ethnic group of Estonia or someone descended from such people.
Any person from Estonia or someone descended from such people.
The Uralic language that is the official language of Estonia.

main_definition: ( countable ) A person of the indigenous ethnic group of Estonia or someone descended from such people.
secondary_definitions: ( countable , rare ) Any person from Estonia or someone descended from such people.
( uncountable ) The Uralic language that is the official language of Estonia.
